(61, 4, 15, 14, 'T11', 'T11-Bluetooth-FM-Transmitter-Car-Charger-Car-Kit-Adapter', 't11-bluetooth-fm-transmitter-car-charger-car-kit-adapter', '<p><br />\r\n<strong>Features:</strong><br />\r\n- A multifunctional Bluetooth adapter with a built-in FM transmitter, microphone and USB charging port<br />\r\n- Simple installation: just plug the Bluetooth FM transmitter into your car&#39;s cigarette socket and set the frequency<br />\r\n- Easily view the current voltage, frequency, track or caller ID thanks to the 1.44-inch LED display<br />\r\n- Use one port to stream music directly from your USB stick and the other to charge your device<br />\r\n- Stream music from four different sources: via Bluetooth, from your USB drive, a TF card, or via 3.5mm aux<br />\r\n- Switch between the four music sources by pressing the &quot;M&quot; button on the Bluetooth car kit<br />\r\n- The integrated microphone allows you to answer/make calls hands-free<br />\r\n- The CVC technology enhances the audio experience and suppresses noise<br />\r\n- Ideal for older cars that don&#39;t have Bluetooth music streaming built in<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Specifications:</strong><br />\r\n- Bluetooth Version: V3.0+EDR<br />\r\n- Frequency: 20Hz - 20KHz<br />\r\n- USB Charging Output: 5V 2.1A<br />\r\n- Working Current: 45mA (Max)<br />\r\n- Stand-by Current: 25mA (Max)<br />\r\n- FM: 87.5MHz-108.0MHz<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Package includes:</strong><br />\r\n- 1 x T11 Bluetooth FM Transmitter &amp; 2.1A Car Charger<br />\r\n- 1 x 3.5mm Audio Cable<br />\r\n- 1 x User Manual</p>', 'Enjoy superior sound quality when driving and recharge your device on-the-go with the T11 Bluetooth FM transmitter & 2.1A car charger.This multifunctional Bluetooth car kit lets you stream music from four different sources and has two USB ports for connecting your charging cable or a USB drive. Other than that, this Bluetooth car kit allows you to answer calls hands-free thanks to its built-in microphone.', NULL, 9